'''''Star Wars'' 95''' is the ninety-fifth issue of the [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] series [[Star Wars (1977)|''Star Wars'']]. It was written by [[Mary Jo Duffy]], illustrated by [[Cynthia Martin]], and first published on [[February 12]], [[1985]] by [[Marvel Comics]]. The issue features the story "'''No Zeltrons'''," which culminates in a climactic [[Skirmish on Kinooine|duel]] between [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and the [[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lady]] [[Lumiya]].

==Publisher's summary==
''There's a new Dark Lord in the galaxy, and she's out for Luke's head! Not only must Luke fight Lumiya, he must also deal with who and, more dangerously, what she really is!''

